metadata.name: The Great Escape
metadata.description:
L8bringer has finally managed to escape from her painting after years of dreaming of freedom. She gazes at the frame that she existed in, and sees an imprint of the lamp that she carries.

Light has left a beautiful mark. She takes it as a sign, and is determined to bring hope & light to the world around her.

"Now that I am free
Watch me illuminate

The world around me
Hope is what makes us great

Together, we can vanquish the darkness"
